items.title: Business News Live: Paramount Dye Tec, Subam Papers IPOs to list today, check all the details here
items.description: Business news live: Paramount Dye Tec and Subam Papers IPOs list today, with price bands of Rs 111-117 and Rs 144-152 per share, respectively. Both IPOs saw bids open from September 30 to October 3, 2024.

items.title: Spectrum payment: Vodafone Idea says it continues to be engaged with DoT for waiver of bank guarantee
